metadata.name: Zelos, The Aether Born
metadata.description: Zelos is the leader of the Chronos empire, a shadowy organization that controls the flow of time. He is a powerful psionic who can manipulate the aether, the energy that flows through all things. He is a master of subterfuge and has a network of spies and agents who carry out his will. He is rumored to be immortal, and his goals are shrouded in mystery. Some say he seeks to control all of time, others say he wants to destroy it.
